g.text: Level 3 FE Diagram for Searching Staff
Sends HTTP Request to get staff by Id
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Tries to get all Staffs data
Sends HTTP Request to get all Specializations
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Displays initial list and asks for the data to filter the Staffs
Sends the data to filter the Staffs
The data can be First Name and/or Last Name and/or
Full Nameand/or Email and/or Specialization Name
Sends HTTP request to search staff with filters
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Validates the data and tries to list the filtered staff
